Migrate the 1927-line custom CSS file (apps/web/src/index.css) to Tailwind CSS 4.0 with design tokens and utility classes.

## Why This Matters
- Tailwind 4.0 (Jan 2025) offers 5x faster builds with native CSS cascade layers
- CSS-first configuration reduces complexity
- Consistent design tokens improve maintainability
- Per research: "Modern CSS features: @property support, container queries, wide-gamut colors"
- Currently using 1927 lines of custom CSS that duplicates what Tailwind provides

