## Device-Code Flow Technical Specification

### State Machine

```typescript
type DeviceCodeState = 
  | { status: 'idle' }
  | { status: 'initiating', provider: ProviderId }
  | { status: 'pending', code: string, verificationUrl: string, expiresAt: Date, pollInterval: number }
  | { status: 'polling', code: string, attempt: number, maxAttempts: number }
  | { status: 'authorized', profile: AccountProfile }
  | { status: 'expired', retryable: true }
  | { status: 'denied', reason: string, retryable: boolean }
  | { status: 'error', error: GatewayError, retryable: boolean };
