## Problem Statement

The Gateway needs a comprehensive frontend dashboard for RU (Repo Updater) that provides visibility into fleet status, sync operations, and agent-sweep sessions with real-time updates.

## Background

Users need to:
1. View fleet health at a glance
2. See individual repo status and sync history
3. Monitor sync operations in progress
4. Manage agent-sweep sessions (view, approve plans, monitor execution)
5. Configure fleet groups and settings

